t/team-coordination.js` and using it only in `assignTaskToThread`, `claimTaskForThread`, `heartbeatThread`, `blockTaskForThread`, and `completeTaskForThread`.\n- Keep the execution boundary fixed: do not expand that slice into mailbox UI changes, stale-lease recovery, or broader supervisor flow changes.\n- Keep the closure rule fixed: the resolver slice should close both Task 6 thread-validation checkboxes together, because the resolver is the concrete implementation of the stale-thread rejection outcome.\n- If the hardening pass finds risk to current stable behavior, pause feature expansion and route the following pass to containment or rollback-friendly isolation.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
